window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When a seductive demon begins using her evil daughters to kill tourists, Ring Hardigan will use his knife, his two girlfriends, and his wits to find the elusive beast and put a blade in her. Through clues and the story of a man claiming to be the demon’s father, the hunters become the hunted - and everyone around them is at risk from Elizabeth and her bloodthirsty family.</p> <p>As a hurricane bears down on the beaches, the demon hunters will finally get what they’ve been wanting all along: blood.</p> <p>But whose will it be? Theirs or the demon’s?</p> <p>Warning: This gritty urban fantasy harem contains lust, revenge, and evil. Proceed with care.</p>"; 
